@page "/"

<PageTitle>Shiny Blazor Controls</PageTitle>

<h1>Shiny Blazor Controls</h1>
<p>Foundational set of controls ported from <code>Shiny.Maui.Controls</code> to Blazor WebAssembly.</p>

<ul class="feature-list">
    <li><strong>Pill</strong> — semantic status badges (Success, Info, Warning, Caution, Critical)</li>
    <li><strong>Fab</strong> — floating action button</li>
    <li><strong>FabMenu</strong> — speed-dial style action menu</li>
    <li><strong>Cells</strong> — Button, Label, Switch, Checkbox, SimpleCheck, Radio, Entry, Picker, TextPicker, NumberPicker, DatePicker, TimePicker, DurationPicker, Command, Custom</li>
    <li><strong>TableView</strong> — settings-style sectioned list with cascading styles</li>
    <li><strong>MarkdownView</strong> — full Markdown renderer (Markdig)</li>
    <li><strong>MermaidDiagram</strong> — render flowcharts and diagrams (mermaid.js via JS interop)</li>
</ul>
